{"tid":1317191,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【長期戰】運動要贏，就要拉攏到中產既支持,要同佢地講埋\"納稅人錢送中“","createTime":"2019-07-14T17:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-14T19:21:32.000Z","uid":107613,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9bceef8ffa6fba1b281680758aa6df64b81c398a","tid":1317191,"uid":107613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17:44:24.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家聽聽從1：04：00 至 1：09：05 既5分鍾論述，好有前瞻性！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jcGEG_qfeLk?t=3842\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FjcGEG_qfeLk%3Ft%3D3842&d=ljlrpVqLOnAgFN3Ei6%2BgJ%2FilxGv0e2UEk%2F7kpEYl8nk%3D&h=b281151c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/jcGEG_qfeLk?t=3842</a><br />\n<br />\n點解我們69，612贏到，係當中有好多平時政治冷感的中產都走埋出黎,班中產平時淨係care <strong>錢</strong>同埋<strong>民生</strong>，我地要將抗爭既議題拉番落<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">民生</span></strong> (屯門公園就係好例子）!!!!!<br />\n<br />\n1)迫班保皇黨同政府表態明日大嶼計劃，點解要倒納稅人錢落咸水海？？<br />\n2）點解唔解決公立醫院長期迫爆問題? 150單程証仲要搶幾多香港人資源?<br />\n3)中環海濱用地點解要俾解放軍?點解唔俾返公共空間港人跑步/放狗?<br />\n<br />\n要將<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">民生議題政治化</span>!!! 只要保皇黨同政府係呢個風頭火勢講錯野,就會更加令到佢地係11月選舉出現大敗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">We cannot let our neighbor die in vain</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/65834541_2308618575891619_5971472260614062080_n_aAJ7s_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F65834541_2308618575891619_5971472260614062080_n_aAJ7s_1200x0.jpg&h=8619a39b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">外爭人權，外除港賊</span></span>"},{"pid":"0ca32de704b205a59a8d26d33c53c64cd486c536","tid":1317191,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T17: